features: EXPERIENCE TWO FLAVORS: Experience the perfect combo with our classic Mint flavor and the exciting new BOLD Mint flavor. Get ready to enjoy 20 pieces of our iconic Mint Flavor, along with an additional 20 pieces of the refreshing BOLD Mint Flavor – a combined total of 40 travel size mouthwash packets.

JET-SETTER APPROVED: Travel smart and stress-free with our TSA-approved mini mouthwash packets instead of bottles. Enjoy fresh breath and a clean mouth wherever your travels take you! Perfect portability for trips by plane, hotel stays, camping trips, or business pursuits.

SPILL-PROOF, MOUTHWASH PACKETS: No more worries about stains and spills ruining your clothes! Our travel mouthwash individual packets are formulated with a natural liquid formula that's free from artificial dyes, colors, or harsh ingredients that can cause staining. And that's not all - our travel packets are also gluten-free and have not been tested on animals!

NEVER-ENDING POTENTIAL: Go Travel Mouthwash packets have endless potentials with their various uses, such as providing a refreshing solution during travel, enhancing guests' stays in hotels and Airbnbs, offering a convenient bulk mouthwash option for gyms and medical facilities, and providing a practical solution for maintaining good oral hygiene in food service settings, restrooms, and so many more!

ELEVATE YOUR GUEST EXPERIENCE: Our packets provide a convenient and luxurious solution for guests to freshen their breath and maintain oral hygiene. By providing Go Mouthwash Individual Packets, you can enhance your guests' stay and make them feel appreciated, leaving a lasting impression.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars EASY TO TRAVEL WITH
reviews.reviewText: These little packets are PERFECT for vacation for when you don't want to check your luggage at the airport, but still need to have mouthwash on hand. They take up no room and fit easily in any purse, pocket, fanny pack, etc. Just great for anytime you want to freshen up your breath. The flavor is great too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: They take up very little room, less room than the travel type you buy at a drug store, it’s handy after your lunch at work, buy a disposable tooth brush just to get those pieces of food that get stuck between your teeth while you use the mouth wash, it’ll feel even fresher!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for a trip, but they come in handy for on the go. May need more before my trip.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for on-the-go…
reviews.reviewText: One star removed because of the expense.The Bold is a bit spicy, but does the trick! There is a mouthful of wash in each packet. I don’t know if it’s just me, but the packets are really difficult to open. The convenient size is great for travel, work, or whenever. I will be purchasing again.
